Cause I'm BestDriver

00:03:23.437 --> 00:03:29.884
I'm the best driver

00:03:31.381 --> 00:03:38.045
Cause I'm BestDriver

00:03:39.389 --> 00:03:46.054
I'm the best driver

00:03:48.341 --> 00:03:51.318
Why do I keep ending up on unpaved roads

00:03:52.245 --> 00:03:55.437
Why do I keep stopping at crossroads without lights

00:03:56.181 --> 00:03:59.813
Trying to hide the regret and desperation that made me try

00:03:59.813 --> 00:04:03.477
Why should my courage have to
be compared to someone else's

00:04:04.140 --> 00:04:05.696
Yes, it's okay to let others pass me by

00:04:05.696 --> 00:04:07.926
To be stuck inside a long tunnel

00:04:07.926 --> 00:04:09.797
Let the soles of my shoes wear out

00:04:09.797 --> 00:04:11.925
Let the wheels keep rolling

00:04:12.180 --> 00:04:15.451
And I ask how to dream a more dramatic life

00:04:15.451 --> 00:04:17.413
Don't stop, keep the foot on the accelerator

00:04:17.413 --> 00:04:19.445
Like spitting out the fumes

